Fri Apr 10 06:18:41 PM EDT 2026
XATS2JS-srcgen2.2 is another version of XATS2JS;
it makes use of some IR of XATS2CC (xats2cc/srcgen1/intrep0).
It does tail-recursion optimization and should be superseding
XATS2JS-srcgen2.1 for pretty much any common purpose.
